Holdgate has received numerous awards and honours for his work.<ref name="Debretts">[http://www.debretts.com/people/biographies/browse/h/447/Martin%20Wyatt+HOLDGATE.aspx Sir Martin Holdgate, CB] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130720074908/http://www.debretts.com/people/biographies/browse/h/447/Martin%20Wyatt+HOLDGATE.aspx |date=20 July 2013 }}, Debretts 'People of Today', accessed 16 February 2010</ref>

